This blend is crafted with a balanced 50/50 VG/PG ratio, enhancing both flavor intensity and vapor production. Ideal for fruit lovers, this e-liquid comes in a 30mL unicorn bottle with nicotine salt formulation available in 20mg and 50mg strengths, ensuring a satisfying and smooth hit every time. Dive into a lush, fruity escape with every draw from Black Dragon - HQD Salts.
BLACK DRAGON - HQD SALTS - 30ML FEATURES:
• FLAVOR PROFILE: Fruit | Blackberry | Dragonfruit
• BOTTLE CAPACITY: 30mL Unicorn Bottle
• VG: 50%
• PG: 50%
• FORMULATION: Nicotine Salts
INCLUDES:
• 1 Black Dragon - HQD Salts - 30mL
AVAILABLE OPTIONS:
• 20mg
• 50mg
CALIFORNIA PROPOSITION 65 Warning: This product contains nicotine, a chemical known to the state of California to cause birth defects or other reproductive harm.
